Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:01.78,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\k1}拜{\k1}托{\k1}请{\k1}不{\k1}要{\k1}停{\k1}下{\k1}来
Comment: 0,0:00:01.78,0:00:05.14,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\k1}S{\k1}t{\k1}r{\k1}a{\k1}w{\k1}b{\k1}e{\k1}r{\k1}r{\k1}y{\k1}·{\k1}发{\k1}射{\k1}·{\k1}S{\k1}t{\k1}r{\k1}a{\k1}w{\k1}b{\k1}e{\k1}r{\k1}r{\k1}y{\k1}·{\k1}l{\k1}i{\k1}e
Comment: 0,0:00:05.24,0:00:07.83,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\k1}我{\k1}会{\k1}让{\k1}你{\k1}屈{\k1}服
Comment: 0,0:00:21.67,0:00:24.47,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\k1}跪{\k1}下{\k1}在{\k1}此{\k1}立{\k1}下{\k1}誓{\k1}言
Comment: 0,0:00:24.80,0:00:28.60,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\k1}伸{\k1}出{\k1}的{\k1}指{\k1}尖{\k1} {\k1}A{\k1}n{\k1}y{\k1}t{\k1}i{\k1}m{\k1}e{\k1},{\k1} {\k1}t{\k1}o{\k1}u{\k1}c{\k1}h{\k1}i{\k1}n{\k1}g{\k1} {\k1}y{\k1}o{\k1}u
Comment: 0,0:00:28.60,0:00:31.41,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\k1}不{\k1}能{\k1}被{\k1}知{\k1}道{\k1}的{\k1}秘{\k1}密{\k1}任{\k1}务
Comment: 0,0:00:31.74,0:00:37.32,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\k1}二{\k1}人{\k1}犯{\k1}下{\k1}的{\k1}深{\k1}重{\k1}罪{\k1}孽{\k1}…
Comment: 0,0:00:37.85,0:00:41.41,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\k1}循{\k1}环{\k1}往{\k1}复{\k1}的{\k1}世{\k1}界{\k1}线
Comment: 0,0:00:42.63,0:00:46.97,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\k1}「{\k1}我{\k1}需{\k1}要{\k1}你{\k1}，{\k1}我{\k1}需{\k1}要{\k1}你{\k1}」{\k1}这{\k1}是{\k1}秘{\k1}密
Comment: 0,0:00:51.75,0:00:55.52,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\k1}拜{\k1}托{\k1}请{\k1}不{\k1}要{\k1}停{\k1}下{\k1}来
Comment: 0,0:00:55.64,0:00:59.17,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\k1}你{\k1}与{\k1}我{\k1}共{\k1}同{\k1}奏{\k1}响{\k1}的{\k1}旋{\k1}律
Comment: 0,0:01:05.66,0:01:09.61,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\k1}时{\k1}刻{\k1}都{\k1}要{\k1}在{\k1}我{\k1}身{\k1}边
Comment: 0,0:01:09.61,0:01:12.97,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\k1}S{\k1}t{\k1}r{\k1}a{\k1}w{\k1}b{\k1}e{\k1}r{\k1}r{\k1}y{\k1}·{\k1}发{\k1}射{\k1}·{\k1}s{\k1}t{\k1}r{\k1}a{\k1}w{\k1}b{\k1}e{\k1}r{\k1}r{\k1}y{\k1}·{\k1}l{\k1}i{\k1}e
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,----------ED----------
Comment: 0,0:22:27.69,0:22:32.15,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,その腕に絡んだ時計の針は
Comment: 0,0:22:32.15,0:22:33.84,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,Close-set mind
Comment: 0,0:22:34.00,0:22:38.22,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,狂わないなんて信じていないで
Comment: 0,0:22:40.17,0:22:45.54,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,進もうと急かすような秒針
Comment: 0,0:22:44.54,0:22:46.54,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,Close-set mind
Comment: 0,0:22:46.54,0:22:51.19,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,巻き戻そう 抓んだ竜頭回し
Comment: 0,0:22:52.33,0:22:55.28,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,奇想夢譚になっていく
Comment: 0,0:22:55.48,0:22:58.32,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,曖昧が依然あるなら
Comment: 0,0:22:58.53,0:23:01.50,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,触れて確かめてしまえばいいよ
Comment: 0,0:23:01.67,0:23:04.22,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,現実を脱がせて
Comment: 0,0:23:04.45,0:23:07.71,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,Let me hightail it out of here
Comment: 0,0:23:07.91,0:23:10.86,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,繰り返すほど牴牾しい
Comment: 0,0:23:11.05,0:23:17.05,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,儚いって知りながら 求めてしまう
Comment: 0,0:23:17.25,0:23:20.40,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,背徳の夢
Comment: 0,0:22:27.69,0:22:32.15,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,缠绕在你腕上的时针
Comment: 0,0:22:34.00,0:22:38.22,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,毋庸置疑会行至疯狂
Comment: 0,0:22:40.17,0:22:45.54,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,仿佛在催促前行的秒针
Comment: 0,0:22:46.54,0:22:51.19,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,拧动发条 让我们逆转时光吧
Comment: 0,0:22:52.33,0:22:55.28,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,坠入梦幻奇谭
Comment: 0,0:22:55.48,0:22:58.32,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,若暧昧仍旧存在
Comment: 0,0:22:58.53,0:23:01.50,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,亲自触碰来确认这一切
Comment: 0,0:23:01.67,0:23:04.22,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,褪去现实的桎梏
Comment: 0,0:23:07.91,0:23:10.86,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,越是重演便越显矛盾
Comment: 0,0:23:11.05,0:23:17.05,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,明知虚幻 却仍执于追寻
Comment: 0,0:23:17.25,0:23:20.40,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,这场背德之梦
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,----------STAFF----------
